{"tid":1205310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重申！今次真係萬眾一心 千祈唔好做啲野令人有機會抹黑分化我地","createTime":"2019-06-11T17:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T00:27:19.000Z","uid":1251,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb40f3670e97b1ae9998dc65d24165cfc02b5ac","tid":1205310,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:58:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">塞地鐵係百害而無一利</span><br />\n<br />\n今次件事其實得柒婆一個想條例過到<br />\n連班建制都唔支持條例通過<br />\n一過左對佢地只有壞影響<br />\n經濟又影響到<br />\n票源又少左<br />\n分分鐘連屋企人既外國passport都冇埋<br />\n<br />\n柒婆就攞晒彩去習總個度領功<br />\n建制班友就俾柒婆當屍底咁踩住上<br />\n<br />\n建制今次都係焗住要投票支持<br />\n如果有一個理由俾佢落台唔去投/投唔到<br />\n佢地應該求之不得<br />\n<br />\n所以我地只需要製造一個佢地投唔到票既狀況就得<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請集中目標：包圍立法會阻止佢地投票</span></span>"},{"pid":"1ef757c8d2fe016f34b96f77d5f38849ee5bf6db","tid":1205310,"uid":220236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:59:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99231b58da5d8d0e7aa0a5a17b35cf8c14c53a4a","tid":1205310,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:00:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"adb70ceec623398caa38e77dc8550bf3f3534704","tid":1205310,"uid":216421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:00:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母 千奇唔好塞地鐵，一個二個比個冇source黑驚wtsapp post慫恿到，冇支援想點打啊<br />\n塞地鐵都唔係聽日啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">有理由懷疑個wtsapp post 係鬼係黎搗亂，你睇下有幾多討論先啦，已經中咗驚犬計,比人分化</span></span>"},{"pid":"cda5652e48eea21abd5458ceb000149129d5d3af","tid":1205310,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"